This is a NodeMCU ESP8266 based ThermalCycler.

Electronic Parts include:
1) NodeMCU ESP8266
2) 4 Channel Relay
3) DC-DC Buck Converter
4) KY-013 Thermistor Module
5) TEC1- 12710 Peltier Module
6) A Vertical PC Cooling Heatsink with Fan
6) 12V 20A SMPS
7) 40W cartridge heater (for heated LID)
8) Thermostat Module (for heated LID)

It is capable of holding 16 0.2ml Tubes at a time. An Aluminium Heater Block has been machined for this.
